    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a standard action, you can assume the form of a Small magma elemental, as @Compendium[pf1.spells.pawbnw1nm4f0b98e]{Elemental Body I}. You gain the same abilities as if you had chosen an earth elementalâ€™s form, except your earth glide functions as the earth glide ability of a magma elemental.</p>\n<p>At 9th level, you can assume the form of a Medium magma elemental, as @Compendium[pf1.spells.yldjnorgbx4jsldz]{Elemental Body II}.</p>\n<p>At 11th level, you can assume the form a Large magma elemental, as @Compendium[pf1.spells.hd32fuc6e7j4isbn]{Elemental Body III}.</p>\n<p>At 13th level, you can assume the form of a Huge magma elemental, as @Compendium[pf1.spells.v42t5kpxc8mvd615]{Elemental Body IV}.</p>\n<p>You can use this ability once per day, but the duration is 1 hour per oracle level.</p>\n<p>You must be at least 7th level to choose this revelation.</p>"
